bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[center]
[wave][shake][color=brown]DEETS[/color][/shake][/wave] by
[color=pink][url=https://hatoving.neocities.org]hatoving[/url][/color]

~~~~~~

Developed and programmed by
[wave][shake][font_size=37][color=pink][url=https://hatoving.neocities.org]hatoving[/url][/color], [color=orange][url=https://juici.dev]Juicimated[/url][/color][/font_size][/shake][/wave]


Voice of \"Mystical Honse\"
[wave][shake][font_size=37][color=forest_green][url=https://www.image-line.com]FL Studio[/url][/color][/font_size][/shake][/wave]


Voice of \"Horse\"
[wave][shake][font_size=37][color=pink][url=https://hatoving.neocities.org]hatoving[/url][/color], [color=dodger_blue][url=https://bsky.app/profile/ca-r.bsky.social]ca850[/url][/color][/font_size][/shake][/wave]


Voice of \"Haykeeper\"
[wave][shake][font_size=37][color=pink][url=https://hatoving.neocities.org]hatoving[/url][/color][/font_size][/shake][/wave]


OG voice of \"Mystical Honse\", \"Horse\"
[wave][shake][font_size=37][color=cyan][url=https://www.youtube.com/@BlueBen8]BlueBen8[/url][/color][/font_size][/shake][/wave]


Ambient tracks and music by
[wave][shake][font_size=37][color=dodger_blue][url=https://bsky.app/profile/ca-r.bsky.social]ca850[/url][/color][/font_size][/shake][/wave]
[wave][color=gray]Canon in Horse[/color][/wave]


Models used:

[wave]Doorway Front by [color=green]Kenney[/color]
L Shaped Desk by Zsky [CC-BY] via [color=orange]Poly Pizza[/color]
Executive Chair by Zsky [CC-BY] via [color=orange]Poly Pizza[/color]
Key by \"Poly by Google\" [CC-BY] via [color=orange]Poly Pizza[/color][/wave]



Ending cutscene visuals inspired by:

[wave][color=RED]UNDERTALE[/color] by Toby Fox[/wave]



Music used that isn't mine:

[wave]\"[/wave]Kevin Macleod ~ Aftermath[wave]\"[/wave]
[wave]\"[/wave]Kevin Macleod ~ Killing Time[wave]\"[/wave]



Fonts used:
[wave]
[font=\"res://Fonts/Munson_Roman.otf\"]Munson[/font] by Paul Miller
[/wave]


Various sound effects from:

[wave][color=maroon]FreeSound.org[/color][/wave]



Programs used:
[wave][color=deep_sky_blue]Godot Engine by The Godot Foundation[/color][/wave]
[wave][color=blue]Audacity by The Audacity Team[/color][/wave]
[wave][color=forest_green]FL Studio by Image-Line[/color][/wave]
[wave][color=green]REAPER by Cockos[/color][/wave]
[wave][color=white]Aseprite by Igara Studio S.A[/color][/wave]
[wave][color=sky_blue]Blockbench by Jannisx11[/color][/wave]


Plugins for Godot used:

[wave][color=orange]Newgrounds API[/color] by jefvel[/wave]


Various stock photos where used from:

[wave]Unisplash[/wave]


If I missed some assets, or if I've accidentally used yours without permission, then please contact me! I want to credit everything that I use as much as I can, and the last thing I want to do is not crediting anyone properly.

[font_size=27]Thank you for playing!

"

